OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776739028
OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe FA cup medal won by footballer
OL,7,FSteve Nicol after he helped carry
OL,8,FLiverpool FC to victory during the
OL,9,F1985 to 1986 season is expected to
OL,10,Ffetch as much as #20,000 when it is
OL,11,Foffered at auction.
OL,13,FThe medal, which carries an estimate
OL,14,Fof #10,000 to #20,000, marks the first
OL,15,FFA Cup title of Nicol's career, and
OL,16,Fwas won after a 3-1 victory for
OL,17,FLiverpool after a nail-biting match
OL,18,Fagainst Everton FC at Wembley Stadium
OL,19,Fin 1986.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
