OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776739028
OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,FIt is leading the collection of
OL,7,Fmemorabilia from the former
OL,8,Ffootballer's highly successful career,
OL,9,Fwhich is set to go under the hammer at
OL,10,FPropstore auction house in London
OL,11,Flater this month.
OL,13,FThe Scottish-born footballer's
OL,14,FEuropean Cup winners' medal, which was
OL,15,Fwon after Liverpool's tense 1984 match
OL,16,Fagainst Roma in the Stadio Olimpico in
OL,17,FRome, is expected to sell for #8,000
OL,18,Fto #16,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
