PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776739028
OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe Football Writers' Association
OL,7,F(FWA) Footballer of the Year award,
OL,8,Fwon by Nicol in 1989 for his high-
OL,9,Flevel performance at the Premier
OL,10,FLeague club, is also up for sale and
OL,11,Fis expected to fetch #2,000 to #4,000.
OL,13,FOther items set to go under the hammer
OL,14,Finclude the shirt he wore during the
OL,15,FScotland v England Rous Cup game in
OL,16,F1988, which is hoped to fetch #1,000
OL,17,Fto #2,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
