PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776739028
OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe auction is taking place from April
OL,7,F21 to May 14 and will also include the
OL,8,Fshirt worn by Nicol during Liverpool
OL,9,Fand Everton's FA Cup final match in
OL,10,F1989, which is expected to sell for
OL,11,F#3,000 to #6,000.
OL,13,FNicol, 64, is best known for his 13-
OL,14,Fyear tenure at Liverpool FC, which saw
OL,15,Fhim land three FA Cup victories and
OL,16,Fscore 46 goals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
