OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776739028
OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,FNicol has also played for teams
OL,7,Fincluding Notts County FC, Sheffield
OL,8,FWednesday and Doncaster Rovers, and
OL,9,Femigrated to the United States in 1999
OL,10,Fto pursue a career in Major League
OL,11,FSoccer (MLS).
OL,13,FSpeaking about the upcoming auction,
OL,14,FNicol said: "I've been fortunate to be
OL,15,Fpart of some incredible teams
OL,16,Fthroughout my career, from
OL,17,Frepresenting Scotland to my years with
OL,18,FLiverpool.
OL,26,@vD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
