OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776739028
OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,F"These items hold many personal
OL,7,Fmemories, but I'm pleased to be
OL,8,Foffering them through Propstore, where
OL,9,Fthey'll go to fans and collectors who
OL,10,Fshare that passion for the game.
OL,12,F"It means a great deal to know they'll
OL,13,Fcontinue to be appreciated for years
OL,14,Fto come."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@IO]
