PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776739028
OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,FThe event will offer more than 50 lots
OL,7,Favailable for worldwide bidding, with
OL,8,Fother items up for sale, including an
OL,9,FMLS all-star game shirt signed by
OL,10,Fstars including Sir David Beckham and
OL,11,FLandon Donovan, which has a pre-sale
OL,12,Festimate of #400 to #800.
OL,14,FAlastair McCrea, Propstore specialist,
OL,15,Fsaid: "This is a fantastic collection
OL,16,Fthat really captures the breadth of
OL,17,FSteve Nicol's career, from domestic
OL,18,Fand European success with Liverpool to
OL,19,Fhis time on the international stage.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
