OL,3,CSteve Nicol's FA Cup medal could fetch
OL,4,Cup to #20,000 at memorabilia auction
OL,6,F"It's not often that material of this
OL,7,Fquality and provenance becomes
OL,8,Favailable, and Propstore expects
OL,9,Fstrong interest from collectors and
OL,10,Ffootball fans around the world."
